        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Asks for translation of colonization law.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>Trinity Taskasito</placeName> <date when="1825-12-01">1st December 1825</date>.</p>
<p>Dear Sir.</p>

<p>The peculiarity of Interest I feel on the subject induce me to
solicit a favor from you, which from the liberality of your disposition I anticipate will be granted: I should be very glad to receive
from your kindly office by the first safe conveyance a <hi rend="italic">Translated
copy</hi> of the Colonization Laws relating to conditions of Locations of
Lands etc etc in this <placeName>province</placeName></p>

<p>Your complyance will place me under an obligation which will be
most cheerfully reciprocated on the first occasion</p>

<p><persName>George Orr</persName></p>

<p>NB Any charge for the Copy of the Laws I will pay on demand.</p>

<p>[Addressed]: To his Excellency <persName>Colonel Stephen F. Austin</persName> at <placeName>St.
Felipe de Austin <hi rend="italic">Province of Texas</hi></placeName>.</p>


        </div1>
